TopicTitle: Ksp not loading after removing some storage.

Articles.Content:
Hi everybody, My computer recently said that my storage was full. I couldn't save or launch my vehicle so i quit the game and removed some storage. Now when i try to launch ksp, It hangs on a random mod. First it was AOATech/Hornet, So i deleted aoatech, Then it was an mk2 barrel in AviatorArsenal, so i deleted that, THEN it was a magnum in BD Fps.

Thanks.

2 hours ago, siklidkid said:

and removed some storage.

And what is that supposed to mean?
Well the game was REALLY laggy after it said that it was full, so i removed some non important stuff on my computer. Sorry if i wasn't clear.
